item.title: Mexico [Part 1] - Mexico, Baby!
item.author: gupta.karan.11@gmail.com (Karan Gupta)
item.description: After spending about two months in the USA, mostly with Di and Praval, we took a flight out of Vegas to Mexico City. When our travel plans had been detoured towards the western hemisphere, we decided to make the most of the time there. While a lot of things were in consideration, including Cuba and South America, we had settled for a couple of months in Mexico.
